\bar H_{n+1}|H_n
Pr(H_{n+1}|H_n) + Pr(\bar H_{n+1}|H_n) = 1
Pr(H_{n+1}|\bar H_n) + Pr(\bar H_{n+1}|\bar H_n) = 1
\begin{bmatrix}Pr(H_{n+1}) \\ Pr(\bar H_{n+1})\end{bmatrix} = \begin{bmatrix}Pr(H_{n+1}|H_n) & Pr(H_{n+1}|\bar H_n)\\1 - Pr(H_{n+1}|H_n) & 1 - Pr(H_{n+1}|\bar H_n)\end{bmatrix} \begin{bmatrix}Pr(H_{n}) \\ Pr(\bar H_{n})\end{bmatrix}
